Symbol.Script_1D:
! const values for parameter: gs_detlevel_3D_m DLEV3D_OFF = 0 DLEV3D_SIMPLE = 1 DLEV3D_DETAILED = 2
! const values for parameter: iPoolShape POOLTYPE_8SHAPED = 1 POOLTYPE_KIDNEY = 2 POOLTYPE_LSHAPED = 3
EPS=0.0001
pdt=0.05 vb=0.2
as=abs(a-b)
pdn=0.2 q=1
Symbol.Script_VL:
call "FM_types" parameters all
values{2} "gs_detlevel_3D_m" DLEV3D_DETAILED, `Детальный`, DLEV3D_SIMPLE, `Простой`, DLEV3D_OFF, `Откл.` values{2} "iPoolShape" POOLTYPE_8SHAPED, `Овальная`, POOLTYPE_KIDNEY, `Изогнутая`, POOLTYPE_LSHAPED, `L-образная`
if gs_cont_pen=0 then parameters gs_cont_pen=2 if gs_fill_pen=0 then parameters gs_fill_pen=91 if deck_fill_pen=0 then parameters deck_fill_pen=91 if ladder_fill_pen=0 then parameters ladder_fill_pen=91
values "gs_resol" range [3, ) values "pldp" range [0.4, ) values "wh" range [0, pldp]
if gs_detlevel_3D_m = DLEV3D_SIMPLE then lock "gs_resol"
if ABS(wh)<EPS then !!wh=0 lock "wmat" lock "wpn" endif
if not(ladder) then lock "lmat" lock "lpn" endif
parameters zzyzx=pldp+vb lock "zzyzx"
Symbol.Comment: Бассейн фигурный различных форм и с дополнительной лестницей.
